Quest PDF is a Chrome extension that helps you quickly find PDF files online by focusing your search specifically on PDF documents, making it easier to locate reports, manuals, and research papers without sifting through irrelevant results. Simply click ‘p’ + Tab in your Chrome address bar to start your search for PDF files instantly.

By clicking on the "Add to Chrome" button, I accept and agree to installing the ‘Quest PDF’ Chrome extension and setting Chrome™ default search to that provided by the Yahoo!®, and to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy."
